    <section name="Performance">
      <p>Validate does a lot of varying checks on products from the schema/schematron checks to the ensuring the validity the actual product content.
      We are continuing to improve performance of the software, but there are also things you can do to split up execution in order to maximize your computer's
      processing power to speed up performance.</p>
      
      <subsection name="Metrics">
        <p>To give you a sense of how long it would take to validate individual products with content validation enabled, the following are
